categories: Category:Star Wars: The Old Republic voice actors

nodes.text: Francis Guinan is an American actor. He voiced the Keeper and additional voices in the computer game Star Wars: The Old Republic. He is best known for his role as the patriarch Edgar Teller in the television series Eerie, Indiana.
Guinan has also worked in a number other films and television shows including Speed 2: Cruise Control, The Last Airbender, Constantine, Wikipedia:Star Trek: Enterprise, and Star Trek Voyager.
